‐ No.

39:59.062 --> 40:00.666
‐ No real harm done.

40:00.699 --> 40:02.970
God knows I did worse
in my day.

40:03.004 --> 40:07.045
The funny thing is, the only
thing missing was a doll.

40:07.078 --> 40:09.684
‐ Your teacher said it belonged
to you, Jake.

40:09.717 --> 40:12.022
‐ I caught your act
at school today.

40:12.055 --> 40:13.124
You were incredible.

40:15.495 --> 40:17.098
‐ I'm sorry.

40:17.132 --> 40:18.702
I shouldn't have lied.
I've never done anything

40:18.735 --> 40:20.572
like that before.
‐ Don't worry.

40:20.606 --> 40:21.975
You're not in any kind
of trouble.

40:22.008 --> 40:25.616
I just wanna
get something straight.

40:26.618 --> 40:30.759
So you broke into the school
in the middle of the night

40:30.793 --> 40:32.797
just to get your doll?

40:32.830 --> 40:36.236
‐ Uh, I needed him to practice
for the talent show.

40:36.270 --> 40:43.585
♪ ♪

40:44.621 --> 40:47.158
‐ Hey.
You're all right.

40:55.108 --> 41:00.151
♪ ♪

41:00.184 --> 41:02.957
‐ I'm sorry.

41:02.990 --> 41:06.063
I'm sorry.
I'm sorry.

41:06.096 --> 41:10.238
‐ It was an accident.
It's not your fault.

41:10.271 --> 41:13.477
You okay?

41:13.512 --> 41:16.818
Was he drinking?
‐ Looks like it. Yes.

41:18.555 --> 41:21.661
‐ Thank you.
Come.

41:28.140 --> 41:30.779
‐ Oh, Jake.

41:30.813 --> 41:33.719
What happened to your nose?

41:33.752 --> 41:35.622
‐ I fell.

41:35.656 --> 41:38.260
‐ Oh. Okay.

41:38.294 --> 41:40.899
Thank you, Mr. Wheeler.
Thank you, Jake.

41:40.933 --> 41:42.770
I'm very sorry for your loss.

41:48.648 --> 41:52.690
‐ So what are we calling it?

41:52.723 --> 41:57.566
‐ "Death by misadventure."
For now.

41:57.600 --> 42:04.747
♪ ♪

42:06.250 --> 42:09.156
[thunder booming]

42:25.723 --> 42:27.225
‐ Hi, Jake.

42:27.258 --> 42:28.862
[sighs]

42:31.266 --> 42:34.774
So you're gonna come stay
with us now.

42:34.807 --> 42:36.878
‐ Okay. Thank you.

42:36.911 --> 42:40.586
‐ Can I get you anything?
Are you hungry?

42:40.619 --> 42:41.755
Do you want something to drink?

42:41.788 --> 42:44.627
It's important
to stay hydrated.

42:44.660 --> 42:46.931
‐ No, I'm okay.
Thanks.

42:46.965 --> 42:49.369
‐ Why don't you show Jake
to his room?

42:49.403 --> 42:51.708
‐ Shit.

42:53.812 --> 43:00.893
♪ ♪

43:10.311 --> 43:11.815
‐ So this is yours.

43:15.689 --> 43:16.991
Make yourself at home.

43:17.025 --> 43:19.095
The bathroom's down the hall.

43:19.129 --> 43:23.070
Wi‐Fi password is "EAGLESCOUT,"
all uppercase.

43:24.740 --> 43:27.378
Is there anything else
you need?

43:27.412 --> 43:30.652
‐ I think I'm good.

43:30.686 --> 43:33.758
‐ I want you to know
that we're here for you, Jake.

43:33.792 --> 43:36.196
All of us.
You're not alone.

43:37.833 --> 43:39.336
‐ Thanks, Aunt Bree.

43:47.152 --> 43:49.022
‐ Jake.

43:49.055 --> 43:50.224
What did you mean today?

43:50.258 --> 43:54.032
At the talent show, you know,
about me having a secret.

43:54.065 --> 43:56.370
‐ Um, I was just trying
to be funny.

43:56.403 --> 43:58.240
I didn't‐‐I didn't mean
anything by it.

43:58.274 --> 44:00.746
I'm sorry.

44:00.779 --> 44:02.850
‐ Okay.

44:02.883 --> 44:06.390
Get some rest.

44:06.423 --> 44:13.370
♪ ♪

44:28.300 --> 44:29.369
‐ Talk to me.

44:31.440 --> 44:33.812
I said talk to me, damn it.

44:37.753 --> 44:39.891
All right.
I'm gonna make you‐‐

44:44.366 --> 44:47.171
‐ Hi, I'm Chucky,

44:47.205 --> 44:49.911
and I'm your friend
till the end.

44:49.944 --> 44:52.448
Hidey‐fucking‐ho.

44:52.482 --> 44:55.288
[laughs wickedly]

44:55.321 --> 44:57.058
‐ Holy shit.

44:59.530 --> 45:02.101
‐ I know.

45:02.135 --> 45:04.840
‐ You‐‐you killed him.

45:04.874 --> 45:07.980
You really did it.
‐ We did it, Jake.

45:08.013 --> 45:09.984
‐ I didn't want him dead.

45:10.017 --> 45:11.854
‐ What did you think
I was gonna do,

45:11.888 --> 45:13.490
ask him for a hug?

45:13.525 --> 45:15.228
He got what he deserved.

45:15.261 --> 45:16.965
‐ He‐‐he wasn't always
like that.

45:16.998 --> 45:18.467
When I was younger,
he was really cool.

45:18.500 --> 45:21.173
‐ I know an asshole
when I see one.

45:23.110 --> 45:24.947
‐ After my mom died, he just‐‐

45:24.981 --> 45:26.416
he couldn't deal.

45:26.450 --> 45:29.456
‐ Oh, I thought we were talking
about the cat.

45:31.561 --> 45:34.132
‐ You really are
Charles Lee Ray.

45:34.165 --> 45:37.171
‐ But my friends all call me
Chucky.

45:43.117 --> 45:47.993
Now, let's talk
about that bitch Lexy.

45:48.027 --> 45:50.999
[chilling music]

45:51.033 --> 45:52.435
♪ ♪

45:52.468 --> 45:56.109
[thunder booming]

45:56.143 --> 45:59.316
[ominous music]

45:59.349 --> 46:04.292
♪ ♪

46:04.326 --> 46:06.831
‐ [gasps]

46:06.864 --> 46:08.400
Charles.

